Q. Do all shoppers have to necessarily register before checking out the orders?
<br>
A. Not required. One can place an order without any registration.

<br><br>
Q. How to register on the website?
<br>
A. Click on "Log In" on the right hand corner. Click on "Create a new account".Registration can also be done at the time of checking out of the order.

<br><br>
Q. Which areas are you serving?
<br>
A.Take a look at the delivery tab. In short, currently we are serving East and South Bangalore. Expanding soon to cover all of Bangalore. However, if you are not residing in the above area and want to shop with us, do place an order. We will try our best to deliver.
<br><br>

Q. What are the various payment methods available?
<br>
A. We will accept cash at the time of delivery.

<br><br>

Q. When will you deliver my order?
<br>
A. We have two types of deliveries:
<br>
1. Advantage Delivery on Saturdays and Sundays totally FREE which we encourage you to take advantage of.
<br>
2. Express Delivery within 36 hours of you placing the order at a nominal charge of Rs. 15.
<br>
You can choose the type while placing the order on the website. You can also choose the time of the day at the time of placing an order on the website. The daily cut off time is 5 pm.

<br><br>

Q. Can I cancel an order?
<br>
A. Yes you can cancel your order over the phone before the order cut-off time. Order cut off time is 5 pm on the day you place an order.

<br><br>
Q. Can I amend / update my order after placing it
<br>
A. No, But you can raise another order. Both orders will be delivered

<br><br>

Q. What is the return and refund policy at attachawal?
<br>
A. We will take back any product not upto your liking within reasons.
We do reserve the right to take the final call.

<br><br>
Q. Will I get any discounts for my orders?
<br>
A. Yes, all the products will be below mrp. For special discount you can click on the "Offers" tab.

<br><br>


Q. Is there is any least amount for which I have to place an order?
<br>
A. No there is no limit. You can order only one maggi too.
<br><br>

Q. At what number can I contact you?
<br>
A. You can call us at 9743 743 900.
